==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Obligable
<hw>Ob"li*ga*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Acknowledging, or
complying with, obligation; trustworthy.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The main difference between people seems to be, that one man can
come under obligations on which you can rely, -- is
<qex>obligable</qex>; and another is not.</q>
<rj><qau>Emerson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Obligate</ent>⟦br⟧
